Pre-Game Insights: Pakistan was defeated 3-0 by Sri Lanka in their most recent T20I series.
Both teams have won their most recent games while batting second. Hence we predict that if either side wins the toss before this game, the captain will elect to field first.
The wicket in Dubai has become quicker and simpler to bat on. The spinners will still have some turn, and we anticipate a par score of between 170-180.
